170.title: Infartante Final
170.plot: Mateo, after several attempts, managed to enter the room where Anita and Amanda were. However, the teenager escaped through the window saving her life, while her mother was trapped in the room. Minutes later, Mateo and Catalina tried to find Anita to escape, but were intercepted by the police. They quickly entered an office in the house, where one of them lost his life.

imdb.title: Amanda
plot: _Amanda_ (qv) returns to the Santa Cruz's Hacienda seeking revenge against the four men that raped her when she was just fourteen years old.::Bruno Santa Cruz
